data.description: This 5 bed, 3 bath LIKE NEW beauty is a must see! Enter the main level foyer and walk to the spacious open concept living area. The family room has views to the dining area and kitchen, which boasts grey cabinetry, granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. Large owner's suite on the main level complete with spacious ensuite bathroom and walk in closet. Upstairs there are four well appointed bedrooms and accommodating flex living area that can be used as an office, gym or extra living space. Conveniently located within minutes of shopping, restaurants and I-20. You have to see this one!  *Exclusive lender incentives with Alcova Mortgage/Ciera Jackson NMLS#2522366 Contact agent for lending details.*
